Class SVGTransform

java.lang.Object
org.tquadrat.foundation.svg.type.ValueBase
org.tquadrat.foundation.svg.type.SVGTransform
Direct Known Subclasses:
SVGTransform.SVGMatrix, SVGTransform.SVGRotate, SVGTransform.SVGScale, SVGTransform.SVGSkewX, SVGTransform.SVGSkewY, SVGTransform.SVGTranslate
@ClassVersion(sourceVersion="$Id: SVGTransform.java 1074 2023-10-02 12:05:06Z tquadrat $") @API(status=STABLE, since="0.0.5") public abstract sealed class SVGTransform extends ValueBase permits SVGTransform.SVGMatrix, SVGTransform.SVGRotate, SVGTransform.SVGScale, SVGTransform.SVGSkewX, SVGTransform.SVGSkewY, SVGTransform.SVGTranslate
The abstract base class for the SVG transformations that can be applied to some elements with the attribute "transform".
